    <script type="text/javascript">
        jQuery(function () {
            jQuery('#searchText').keydown(function (e) {
                if (e.which === 13) {
                    SearchMdD('searchText');
                    return false;
                }
            });
        });
        
        function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays, path) {
            var d = new Date();
            d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
            var expires = 'expires=' + d.toUTCString();
            document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + '; ' + expires + '; path=' + path;
        }
        function getCookie(cname) {
            var name = cname + '=';
            var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
            for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                var c = ca[i];
                while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') c = c.substring(1);
                if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
            return '';
        }
        var biscotto = getCookie('cookie-accepted');
        function checkCookie() {
            setCookie('cookie-accepted', '1', 365, '/');
            document.getElementsByTagName('html')[0].className += ' accepted';
        }
        jQuery('a').not('.js-stopCookie, #js-cookieAccept').on('click', function () {
            if (getCookie('cookie-accepted') != '1') {
                checkCookie();
            }
        });
        function cookieControl() {
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(event) {
                if (biscotto == '') {
                    document.getElementsByTagName('html')[0].className += ' cookie';
                } else {
                    document.getElementsByTagName('html')[0].className += ' cookie accepted';
                }
                document.getElementById('js-cookieAccept').onclick = function () {
                    checkCookie();
                }
            });
        }
        cookieControl();
    </script>
